{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/OYikwyUKEWvjlsMIOjpxgqrPIL.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Drama"},{"id":10749,"name":"Romance"}],"homepage":"","id":1396045,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["PL"],"original_language":"pl","original_title":"Powiedz mi, co czujesz","overview":"When an aspiring Polish artist, Patryk, struggles to sell his paintings, he finds himself at Tear Dealer, a unique art project letting people in poverty trade their tears for złoty. Surrounded by sobs and mirrors, however, he is unable to shed a tear. It’s then that he meets Maria, the project’s conceiver and an art therapist from a well-off family. As their romance buds, they swap traumas and art, discovering they may share more than they thought.","popularity":0.9777,"poster_path":"/kolJqRhcJPTYrqbbqOKZ69QGYkB.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":79138,"logo_path":null,"name":"Koskino","origin_country":"PL"},{"id":2466,"logo_path":"/596Eq7ivA0DpNfB5zzDU7yMeTB4.png","name":"Wytwórnia Filmów Dokumentalnych i Fabularnych","origin_country":"PL"},{"id":129370,"logo_path":"/c7OFocnzGIZ86DrcNAzosYNssKZ.png","name":"EC1 Łódź","origin_country":"PL"},{"id":54245,"logo_path":null,"name":"Silesia Film","origin_country":"PL"},{"id":82294,"logo_path":"/z2WExPhsX9E8NGruZrEWosQoC86.png","name":"FIXAFILM","origin_country":"PL"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"PL","name":"Poland"}],"release_date":"2026-09-18","revenue":0,"runtime":94,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Polish","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Tell Me What You Feel","video":false,"vote_average":0.0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]}}